Class SpanningTree

public class SpanningTree
extends Object
    Spanning tree of a molecule. Used to discover the number of cyclic bonds in order to prevent the inefficient AllRingsFinder to run for too long.
    Author:
    Nina Jeliazkova
    Keywords:
    spanning tree, ring finding
